  ### links 
### links to another page such as htpps://www.google.come by clicking to a link 

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>links</title>
    
    </head>
    <body>
        
        <a href="www.google.com">Click her</a>
    </body>


</html>

### list 
@@ there are to type of list 
1.ordred lists
2.unordred lists

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>lists</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        An unordered list:
        <ul>
            <li>one Item </li>
            <li>other item </li>
            <li>Yet other Item</li>
        </ul>
        An ordered list:
        <ol>
            <li>First Item</li>
            <li>Secand Item</li>
            <li>Third Item</li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>

## tables
## table is an structure models you can define a colume and rows

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>Table</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <th>year </th>
                <th> month</th>
                <th>day</th>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>1998</td>
                    <td>oct</td>
                    <td>sunday</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>2000</td>
                    <td>may</td>
                    <td>monday</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </body>

</html>

## form 
## form is an colaction of elements 

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>form</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <form >
            <input type="text"  placeholder="Full_name" name="name">
            <input type="submit">
        </form>
    </body>
</html>

